---
// About Me Section Component
---

<!-- About Me Section -->
<section class="py-20 bg-white border-y-3 border-black relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[40%_60%] gap-10 items-center">
            <!-- Photo Section -->
            <div class="relative">
                <div class="border-3 border-black bg-white p-5 relative">
                    <!-- Corner boxes -->
                    <div class="size-3 bg-white border-2 border-black absolute -top-2 -right-2"></div>
                    <div class="size-3 bg-white border-2 border-black absolute -top-2 -left-2"></div>
                    <div class="size-3 bg-white border-2 border-black absolute -bottom-2 -left-2"></div>
                    <div class="size-3 bg-white border-2 border-black absolute -bottom-2 -right-2"></div>

                    <div class="w-full h-[250px] md:h-[350px] border-2 border-black overflow-hidden">
                        <img src="/founder.jpg" alt="Sebastian Utoiu" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Content Section -->
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
                <h2 class="text-[clamp(1.8rem,5vw,2.5rem)] font-bold leading-tight">
                    <span>About</span>
                    <span class="relative">
                        <span class="absolute bg-[var(--blue)] w-full h-[50%] left-0 bottom-0 z-1"></span>
                        <span class="relative z-5">Me</span>
                    </span>
                </h2>

                <div class="space-y-4 text-[clamp(0.9rem,3.8vw,1.1rem)] leading-relaxed">
                    <p>
                        I'm Sebastian, an IT Consultant with 3+ years of experience, now transitioning into Cloud Architecture with a strong foundation in SQL and database management.
                        My journey in technology has been driven by a passion for solving complex problems and building scalable solutions.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        Currently pursuing a comprehensive Microsoft Azure certification roadmap including AZ-900, SC-900, AZ-104, AZ-305, AI-102, AI-900,
                        DP-100, and beyond. I'm building deep expertise in Cloud Computing, Artificial Intelligence, and Security to become a
                        well-rounded cloud architect.
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        When I'm not diving into cloud technologies, I enjoy exploring the latest trends in DevOps, Infrastructure as Code,
                        and sharing my learning journey through writing and community engagement.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Skills Tags -->
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mt-4">
                    <span class="bg-[var(--yellow)] px-3 py-1 text-sm border border-black">SQL Expert</span>
                    <span class="bg-[var(--blue)] px-3 py-1 text-sm border border-black">Azure Certified</span>
                    <span class="bg-[var(--yellow)] px-3 py-1 text-sm border border-black">Cloud Architecture</span>
                    <span class="bg-[var(--blue)] px-3 py-1 text-sm border border-black">IT Consulting</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
